import React, { Component, Fragment } from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; export default class breadcrumb extends Component { render() { const { title, parent } = this.props; return (

{title}

  1. Home
    2. { parent ?
  2. {parent}
    3. : '' }
  3. {title}
 ) } }
